Package: padthv1-common
Architecture: any
Depends: padthv1-common (= ${binary:Version}),
  ${misc:Depends},
  ${shlibs:Depends},
Description: An old-school polyphonic additive synthesizer - Common files
  An old-school all-digital polyphonic additive synthesizer with stereo fx.
  .
  This package provides files shared by both the LV2 plugin and the
  standalone JACK client application.

